title: You Might Like 'Drunk Donald Trump' More Than The Sober One
text:
You Might Like 'Drunk Donald Trump' More Than The Sober One At least these slurs don't target anyone. 02/09/2017 07:40 am ET Ron Dicker General Assignment Reporter, The Huffington Post 
President Donald Trump reportedly doesn’t drink ― but some may think his actions make it seem like he does. 
“ Jimmy Kimmel Live!” presented another edition of “Drunk Donald Trump” on Wednesday, slowing down video of the president addressing police chiefs to make him sound plastered. 
Many of us might rest easier with this guy next to us at a bar rather than in the Oval Office. Also on HuffPost 37 Funniest 'Jimmy Kimmel Live' Clips 37 37 Funniest 'Jimmy Kimmel Live' Clips 1
